{"tid":2453042,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美資投資管理公司女高層疑逃避檢疫 當局或會通緝","createTime":"2021-03-19T08:04:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T09:26:14.000Z","uid":5195,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b690ee480b33858a10d5fd508138c58863d74771","tid":2453042,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T08:04:42.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎疫情反覆，西營盤健身室URSUS Fitness爆疫群組更蔓延至金融界。《香港01》接獲消息指，一間美資投資管理公司的女高層，被列為密切接觸者須強制檢疫隔離，但卻失蹤，當局或會通緝。消息指，她早前確診的丈夫，亦是另一間美資投行的員工。<br />\n<br />\n該名失蹤的女高層，現年40多歲，在一間美資的投資管理公司香港分公司工作約六七年。《香港01》接獲消息指，她被列為密切接觸者後失蹤，懷疑私下入住一間高級酒店，逃避強制檢疫，當局或通緝。"},{"pid":"a316acdf0440a52056d45062ffe0a73ef6831167","tid":2453042,"uid":108016,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T08:08:54.000Z","msg":"美資投行高層咪又係支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"454e7b36f77fc5b7ac0add9b7e8eae7077d0775f","tid":2453042,"uid":151074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T08:08:55.000Z","msg":"人質外交<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51f70cc198ea287a912c3ea235cf38092c0b1540","tid":2453042,"uid":74442,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T08:09:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DRcC8Zs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDRcC8Zs.jpg&h=ca9c1049&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c37db7066a53d603093e67bd14f23dd74af65d2","tid":2453042,"uid":9193,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T08:46:13.000Z","msg":"垃圾政府夠閪膽通緝咩"},{"pid":"2c0ef436a18549cdefbd45f851514f026b3d4b6b","tid":2453042,"uid":88002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T08:55:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bef462dfd932682ef911b80c30019eef096ca35","tid":2453042,"uid":